Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.74,0:00:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌洗澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.12,0:00:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白 你这样乱动的话没办法洗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 发生了那种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也应该洗澡了吧 妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发会硬硬的 不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.03,0:00:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么要试试这个洗发水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.60,0:00:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从哪里冒出来的啊 吉普莉尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.19,0:00:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是「天翼种」官方指定 以精灵水调配而成的洗发水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.19,0:00:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(206,437)\fs21}Flugel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让您拥有松软 滋润 优秀的发质
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.05,0:00:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\an9\fs21\1c&H414F2A&}精灵水调配而成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.05,0:00:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\an9\fs21\1c&H414F2A&}洗发水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.05,0:00:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\an9\fs21\1c&H414F2A&}保持头发色泽 不伤头发
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.05,0:00:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\an9\fs21\1c&H414F2A&}更容易定型 让您拥有优秀的发质
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.05,0:00:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\an9\fs21\1c&H414F2A&}天翼种官方指定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.19,0:00:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就让我吉普莉尔作为奴隶为主人们洗背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.44,0:00:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,异世界人未知的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.97,0:00:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管她 白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.91,0:00:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙的存在本身就是十八禁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉普莉尔 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.99,0:00:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.38,0:00:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉普莉尔 你只能在那里看着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.73,0:00:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是蒸汽 太折磨人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.97,0:00:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\bord2\shad0\an9\fs27\1c&H346EC6&\3c&HFFFFFF&}哥哥敬仰 膜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.14,0:01:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然以主人的身份完全控制住吉普莉尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.57,0:01:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厉害了 白小姐 我太感动了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.21,0:01:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌已经习惯了这种状况的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(320,300)\pos(672,336)\an7\3c&H4F0999&\1c&HFFFFFF&\bord2\shad0\fs26\fsp5\be5}弃子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(320,300)\pos(657,319)\an7\3c&H4F0999&\1c&HFFFFFF&\bord2\shad0\fs17\fsp3\be5}Sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这里是什么地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是为了主人而准备的厨房
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 杰蒂小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是史蒂芙 是史蒂芬妮·多拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.95,0:03:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对主人以外的「人类种」没有一点兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.95,0:03:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(440,437)\fs21}Imanity
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就叫你哆啦酱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哆啦？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人有话让我传达给哆啦酱你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:09.76,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫史蒂芬妮…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里砂糖和牛油什么的多得是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以随意使用 以上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这么多东西的话就可以做更多点心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就是间接让我做的意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在随便使唤我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过如果没有史蒂芙 我们已经输了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.17,0:03:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 这就是「人类种」的恋爱感情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(443,437)\fs21}Imanity
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋 爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哆啦酱明明没有被命令持续爱着他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.71,0:03:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会出现持续性的影响呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和主人有关的所有事物 我都很感兴趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了 克拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:03:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先要情报？还是先吃饭？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是要我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.08,0:04:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是先穿衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像自从先王的孙女执行新国王的政策之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们的生活也变好了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史蒂芬妮·多拉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 傀儡的傀儡什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是愚王的孙女 不知羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实对羞辱了她这件事耿耿于怀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷偷练习怎样道歉的克拉米也很可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 除了这个没有别的情报吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.16,0:04:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.21,0:04:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有就是新国王得到了一位「天翼种」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.21,0:04:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(605,437)\fs21}Flugel
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及对东部联合有兴趣一事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大致是这些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.24,0:04:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一不小心做多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.85,0:05:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这其实也是为了「人类种」而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.85,0:05:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(502,437)\fs21}Imanity
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.33,0:05:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不是什么恋爱感情…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 吉普莉尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于即将被我征服的兽耳少女乐园——东部联合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你解说一下好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家可能已经完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「兽人种」由于身体特征的差异
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(287,437)\fs21}Warbeast
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长年陷于内部部族斗争的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而在不到半个世纪内 却被突然出现的「巫女」所平定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合并后成为世界第三大国的巨大海洋国家——东部联合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 总而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫耳 狗耳 狐狸耳 兔耳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些活奔乱跳的兽耳们都会成为我的东西是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 赶紧击溃东部联合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此 你经过数千年收集而来的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候发挥作用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾 但那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我直言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是主人们 恐怕也赢不了东部联合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉普莉尔 你是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『    』会输吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(379,437)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.35,0:06:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意思是 我恐怕会辜负您的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我曾一度向东部联合挑战 却输了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在艾尔奇亚背后是东部联合--「兽人种」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(638,437)\fs21}Warbeast
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么确定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.42,0:06:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲尔应该知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱尔文·加尔得过去也曾向东部联合挑战了四次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.15,0:06:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次都输了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 不过输了的都是愚蠢的元老们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两个人能打败「天翼种」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(529,437)\fs21}Flugel
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及打败借助「森精种」力量的我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(453,437)\fs21}Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能解释了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有「兽人种」撑腰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(438,437)\fs21}Warbeast
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能使出「森精种」也无法察觉的骗术就不奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(270,437)\fs21}Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:07:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毋庸置疑 「人类种」不可能战胜上位种族
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:07:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(353,437)\fs21}Imanity
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.16,0:07:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别太小看人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然耍我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不说「天翼种」居然连「森精种」都赢不了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(257,437)\fs21}Flugel
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(500,437)\fs21}Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们到底准备了什么游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东部联合要求的代价是「对游戏内容丧失记忆」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说您明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 难怪赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,98)\fad(0,0)\bord0\shad0\an5\fs27\1c&H417D92&\3c&HFFFFFF&}游戏内容[猜拳]
